*-h, --help* ['TOPIC']::
    Print help TOPIC. *--help* 'topics' will print a list of help
    topics, *--help* 'syntax' summarizes %{NAMEMIXED} syntax,
    *--help* 'manpage' prints the %{NAMEMIXED} manpage.

*-v, --verbose*::
    Verbosely print processing information and configuration file
    checks to stderr.

*-V, --version*::
    Print or show the program version number and exit.

